  "text": "e allergen selecting procedure is listed in Fig 1. e optimized concentrations for a wide range of allergens, allergen sources, and allergen extracts are listed in the original position paper in table S1 [CITATION_1] . Furthermore, optimized allergen preparations are available from vendors. Drug aller gens are typically active in the mg/mL range and can be diluted 5-to 25-fold. If possible, pure active ingredients or injectable intravenous drug preparations should be used since solubilized tablets are complex mixtures of drugs and excipients.",
